Clone this repository

VAGRANT OPTION:

Install ansible roles:
sudo ansible-galaxy install kbrebanov.selinux patrik.uytterhoeven.PostgreSQL-For-RHEL6x geerlingguy.redis geerlingguy.repo-epel jtyr.rabitmq jtyr.config_encoder_filters franklinkim.hosts

Up vagrant machines:
cd vagrant 
vagrant up

Deploy spring xd:
cd ../ansible
ansible-playbook springxd.yml


DOCKER OPTION:

sudo ansible-playbook -i "localhost," -c local  springxd-docker.yml
